Past Reviews

Every week Alaska Burger Blog goes out two times to eat burgers. Every Monday we try a new place out, and order the traditional cheeseburger. We try out the burger, look around the place, and give you an idea how the place is. Here is where you will find archive reviews. Just find the month, and the burger place.
